#~ msgid ""
#~ "**YAML-first** — define robots, sensors, and whole scenes declaratively."
#~ msgstr "**以 YAML 为先** —— 以声明式方式定义机器人、传感器与整个场景。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Built for learning** — reproducible seeding, headless/batch runs, and "
